1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/clair-obscur-expedition-33-lune-weapon-demineur-mine-1851781921\"\u003eRead More\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure id=\"\" data-id=\"e2d0126c3735d669e3c4beaac48157db\" data-recommend-id=\"image://e2d0126c3735d669e3c4beaac48157db\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1894\" data-height=\"1065\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"Verso stands defiantly before the Dualliste.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt=\"Verso stands defiantly before the Dualliste.\" data-link-reference=\"\" data-link-target=\"\" data-syndicationrights=\"true\" data-imagerights=\"fair-use\" data-hide=\"false\" data-hidecredit=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(max-width: 49.94em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_965/e2d0126c3735d669e3c4beaac48157db.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 50em) and (max-width: 63.69em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1315/e2d0126c3735d669e3c4beaac48157db.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 63.75em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1600/e2d0126c3735d669e3c4beaac48157db.jpg\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"Verso stands defiantly before the Dualliste.\" data-chomp-id=\"e2d0126c3735d669e3c4beaac48157db\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-height=\"1065\" data-alt=\"Verso stands defiantly before the Dualliste.\" data-anim-src=\"\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/e2d0126c3735d669e3c4beaac48157db.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eScreenshot: Sandfall Interactive / Justin Clark / Kotaku\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cspan data-id=\"e2d0126c3735d669e3c4beaac48157db\" data-recommend-id=\"image://e2d0126c3735d669e3c4beaac48157db\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1894\" data-height=\"1065\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"Verso stands defiantly before the Dualliste.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eYou might’ve caught a few vibes here and there that the good folks at Sandfall might’ve had a \u003cem\u003eSouls \u003c/em\u003egame or two on the brain while designing \u003cem\u003eClair Obscur.\u003c/em\u003e But right around here is the point where reasonable doubt gets kicked off a skyscraper, because the Dualliste is the most \u003cem\u003eSouls-\u003c/em\u003egame shit ever. It’s a lot of long combos, a second phase, and a lot—and I do mean \u003cem\u003ea lot\u003c/em\u003e—of dying.  - Justin Clark \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/clair-obscur-expedition-33-dualliste-phase-2-verso-1851781495\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/clair-obscur-expedition-33-dualliste-phase-2-verso-1851781495\"\u003eRead More\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure id=\"\" data-id=\"84615e1de68590551dd37aa8acd3539e\" data-recommend-id=\"image://84615e1de68590551dd37aa8acd3539e\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"Yasuke walks up to the wise and other NPCs.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt=\"Yasuke walks up to the wise and other NPCs.\" data-link-reference=\"\" data-link-target=\"\" data-syndicationrights=\"true\" data-imagerights=\"fair-use\" data-hide=\"false\" data-hidecredit=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(max-width: 49.94em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_965/84615e1de68590551dd37aa8acd3539e.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 50em) and (max-width: 63.69em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1315/84615e1de68590551dd37aa8acd3539e.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 63.75em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1600/84615e1de68590551dd37aa8acd3539e.jpg\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"Yasuke walks up to the wise and other NPCs.\" data-chomp-id=\"84615e1de68590551dd37aa8acd3539e\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-height=\"1080\" data-alt=\"Yasuke walks up to the wise and other NPCs.\" data-anim-src=\"\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/84615e1de68590551dd37aa8acd3539e.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eScreenshot: Ubisoft / Justin Clark / Kotaku\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cspan data-id=\"84615e1de68590551dd37aa8acd3539e\" data-recommend-id=\"image://84615e1de68590551dd37aa8acd3539e\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"Yasuke walks up to the wise and other NPCs.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eYou know, Naoe and Yasuke have been killing a whole lot of people lately. Maybe this time, given this mission’s all about two diametrically opposed political factions trying to come to an agreement, they really should dial back down on the violent rhetoric, reach across the aisle, and let diplomacy take its course. - Justin Clark \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/assassins-creed-shadows-wise-boss-yasuke-the-messenger-1851781455\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/assassins-creed-shadows-wise-boss-yasuke-the-messenger-1851781455\"\u003eRead More\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure id=\"\" data-id=\"501dae0f870443cc6e1b3e7a1a82f10c\" data-recommend-id=\"image://501dae0f870443cc6e1b3e7a1a82f10c\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"The side inspection animation for the Ladra SMG in Black Ops 6.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt=\"The side inspection animation for the Ladra SMG in Black Ops 6.\" data-link-reference=\"\" data-link-target=\"\" data-syndicationrights=\"true\" data-imagerights=\"fair-use\" data-hide=\"false\" data-hidecredit=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(max-width: 49.94em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_965/501dae0f870443cc6e1b3e7a1a82f10c.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 50em) and (max-width: 63.69em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1315/501dae0f870443cc6e1b3e7a1a82f10c.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 63.75em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1600/501dae0f870443cc6e1b3e7a1a82f10c.jpg\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"The side inspection animation for the Ladra SMG in Black Ops 6.\" data-chomp-id=\"501dae0f870443cc6e1b3e7a1a82f10c\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-height=\"1080\" data-alt=\"The side inspection animation for the Ladra SMG in Black Ops 6.\" data-anim-src=\"\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/501dae0f870443cc6e1b3e7a1a82f10c.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eScreenshot: Activision / Brandon Morgan / Kotaku\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cspan data-id=\"501dae0f870443cc6e1b3e7a1a82f10c\" data-recommend-id=\"image://501dae0f870443cc6e1b3e7a1a82f10c\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"The side inspection animation for the Ladra SMG in Black Ops 6.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eOne of the most interesting additions joining the fray in \u003cem\u003eCall of Duty: Black Ops 6 Season 3 Reloaded \u003c/em\u003e(what a mouthful!) is the Ladra submachine gun. It’s a fast-firing SMG reminiscent of the Tec-9. But with such a high rate of fire comes a lack of control, which we’ll aim to resolve with the right attachments. While I’m not the best player, I can hold my own, and I know how to build a loadout to suit my purposes, especially in CQB. As proof, I offer you a sweet Ladra loadout in \u003cem\u003eBlack Ops 6\u003c/em\u003e and \u003cem\u003eWarzone \u003c/em\u003ethat saw me achieve nearly 500 kills fast! - Brandon Morgan \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/call-duty-black-ops-6-warzone-wz-ladra-attachments-1851781095\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/call-duty-black-ops-6-warzone-wz-ladra-attachments-1851781095\"\u003eRead More\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure id=\"\" data-id=\"7755631169b9a543d4db84284bb71042\" data-recommend-id=\"image://7755631169b9a543d4db84284bb71042\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"The spires of a Daedric Realm in Oblivion Remastered\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt=\"The spires of a Daedric Realm in Oblivion Remastered\" data-link-reference=\"\" data-link-target=\"\" data-syndicationrights=\"true\" data-imagerights=\"fair-use\" data-hide=\"false\" data-hidecredit=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(max-width: 49.94em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_965/7755631169b9a543d4db84284bb71042.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 50em) and (max-width: 63.69em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1315/7755631169b9a543d4db84284bb71042.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 63.75em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1600/7755631169b9a543d4db84284bb71042.jpg\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"The spires of a Daedric Realm in Oblivion Remastered\" data-chomp-id=\"7755631169b9a543d4db84284bb71042\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-height=\"1080\" data-alt=\"The spires of a Daedric Realm in Oblivion Remastered\" data-anim-src=\"\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/7755631169b9a543d4db84284bb71042.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eScreenshot: Bethesda / Brandon Morgan / Kotaku\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cspan data-id=\"7755631169b9a543d4db84284bb71042\" data-recommend-id=\"image://7755631169b9a543d4db84284bb71042\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"The spires of a Daedric Realm in Oblivion Remastered\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eAs you exit the prologue sewers in \u003cem\u003eOblivion Remastered\u003c/em\u003e, you’re greeted by a whole lot of nothing. There are ruins across the water, a small abandoned dock down the hill, and behind you, an entire city. But where do you go, what do you do, and why should you care about delivering a necklace of all things? There’s a lot the game doesn’t tell you, and we aim to fix that. - Brandon Morgan \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/oblivion-remastered-selling-stolen-goods-scaling-gates-1851781929\u0026#34;,{\u